<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>On updating from 1.9.6 to 1.10.1, output from $this-&gt;view-&gt;escape('£99.99') would render nothing instead of the desired output. It seems this behaviour only effects strings with multi-byte chars (Eg £'s).</p>

